cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
This is an immaculate 2013 Acura ILX with only 11,000 miles on it. Leather seats, full tech package, automatic, v4.
Has some dents and dings but still a beauty with only 100,000 miles on it. Sun-roof, 5 cd changer, custom head unit, gold rims.
